main event: A witness observed an unidentified flying object while getting out of the car at her home in Memphis, Tennessee on 27 December 1960.
interesting points: The object was observed for 9-10 seconds,The sighting involved 3-12 unidentified objects,The witness reported the objects moving east-north,The conclusion drawn from the report was insufficient data for evaluation,The image of the report does not contain any photographs.
witness description: A civilian female who was with her daughter during the observation.
